I think the rangers most concerned about archery auto-attack are those who are  Level 59 +45AA Endless Quiver/ Archery Mastery III types.  The ones who will spend hours at a time clicking 'range attack,' making it impossible to talk while fighting.  For them, archery is a primary means of combat.  I'm not one of them, yet -- but it's my goal as a ranger.  Mebbe in a year or so <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
