Look for some large major wipes and numerous monk deaths on raids as monks relearn how to pull raid targets.  Look for the Dain fight to become nearly impossible without an army of mages for cothing back up out of the well.<br>
<br>
It's definitely a huge major change to the game, but I seriously doubt it's the &quot;phasing out of monks&quot; that Takkon seems to think it will be.  You'll just have to relearn how to pull everything and coincidentally also where and how to setup for raids that rely on pathing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kuladen>kuladen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Greatest,<br>
